  <info>
    <title>Installing Ansible Linux system roles</title>
    <meta name="maintainer" content="amrita.sakthivel@suse.com" its:translate="no"/>
    <abstract>
      <para>
        To install Ansible Linux system roles on a &productname; control node:
      </para>
    </abstract>
  </info>
  <procedure>
      <step>
      <para>
        Install the roles on a control node: </para>
<screen>&prompt.sudo;<command> zypper install ansible-linux-system-roles </command></screen>
    </step></procedure>
    <para>
      The control node is where Ansible and the Linux system roles are installed.
      It is not required to have Ansible or Linux system roles installed on managed nodes.
    </para>
